About five years ago I was cat-sitting for a friend and had to take her cat to the vet, which was Northside Animal Hospital.
I was so impressed with the kindness, patience and efficiency of the staff I started taking my cat there.
I'm the type of customer overall that likes to ask questions like, "Do you know what type of things cause that?
" and "Do you know the actual statistics of success with this procedure/medicine?
" and I LOVE that they always answer patiently and honestly.
